summary: Low performance cost Enb, That is a little gritty and moody.
descriptionHtml:
[b][u][font=Times New Roman][size=6][center]Torva Lux Enb[/center][/size][/font][/u][/b][center][size=4]This is a very simple Enb that has a low performance hit.[/size][/center] [center][size=4]The ideal behind this was to make the game a little darker and grittier.
Made with lighting and weather mods in mind like COC, ELFX, Pure Weather.....Ect.[/size]
[size=6].[/size]
[size=4]Just drop in your Skyrim folder and set in your Skyrim Prefs bFloatPointRenderTarget=0 to =1
then go to [url=http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0108.html]Enbseries V0.108[/url] and extract the d3d9.dll File from the wrapper and add it to your skyrim folder.
.
[/size][size=6][u]Credits[/u] [/size]
